fields.name: Asmodus Kodama
fields.description:
The new Boost Kodama is polished stabilized wood, giving it an extraordinary classic feel!

You will fall in love with all the colors in this unique mod.

fields.name: Asmodus Minikin
fields.description: Minikin 2 Kodama edition is back in stock with a great update! The Minikin 2 Kodama is now powered by a GX-180-UTC, a chipset that packs a punch, has battery saving capabilities and also has a customize-able colored screen.

fields.name: VooPoo Drag v2
fields.description: Powered by dual 18650 batteries, it can reach up to 177W power. As a new generation, the Voopoo Drag 2 177W Kit is lighter and more functional. The Voopoo Drag 2 Mod Adopts the GENE.FIT chip, which is secured by a V0 class fire retardant bridge to block dust, liquid or burning. FIT is a mode that can protect tanks to the fullest with their smart combinations of FIT 1/2/3.

fields.name: ELeaf Pico
fields.description: The iStick Pico, just like its name, is preferable, innovative, compact and outstanding (PICO). Powered by single interchangeable 18650 cell, it provides you with 75W maximum output and switchable VW/Bypass/TC-Ni/TC-Ti/TC-SS/TCR modes.

fields.name: Boxer
fields.description: The classic.A high-end addition to the trending squonk box mod segment, the Boxer Mod Classic DNA 75C BF Squonk 2X700 features a 3D Printed regulated box mod design with the option of utilizing a single 20700 or 21700 battery platform.
